    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example of BMW\u2019s most iconic M-car. At its heart is the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system that delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been addressed and the rear subframe has been reinforced to handle the torque-induced stress on the floor pan. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in the E46 chassis is known for. While the exterior shows honest patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
