      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating that has been conditioned regularly; there is only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, backed by a full service history that includes a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh set of brake pads. The tires have plenty of life left, and the engine starts and idles quietly, providing a smooth, reliable driving experience. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next journey.",
